<comment id="12020" author="712020:8c1c869b-c4be-4401-b6c0-3f69c6178d55" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:32:41 +0900"><ul> <li>The doc supports “language by language” and “batch all languages at once”, but does not define where translated target-language texts come from in MVP.</li> <li>Token estimation is required, but the estimating API, formula, and whether numbers are estimate-only or near-real-time are not defined.</li> <li>“Each POI one by one” is clear, but ordering for multi-language batch is not: language-first, POI-first, or mixed async queue?</li> <li>JP Kanji-to-Hiragana and ZH pronunciation dictionary are required, but the specific service/library/data source is not defined.</li> <li>The Chinese dictionary ownership is unclear: static admin-managed dictionary, system default dictionary, or per-guide glossary?</li> <li>The docs require Firebase upload and DB linking, but not the target schema for generated assets and active-version binding.</li> </ul> </comment>
<comment id="12021" author="712020:8c1c869b-c4be-4401-b6c0-3f69c6178d55" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:35:13 +0900"><p>現在缺的其實是這幾類 schema 定義：</p> <ol> <li>Storage 路徑怎麼命名 <ul> <li>例如是否要像：</li> <li>{{audio/ {guideId}/{spotId}/{lang}/{runId}.mp3}}<br/> #* 還是：<br/> #* {{guides/{guideId} <p>/audio/</p> {lang} <p>/</p> {spotId} <p>/</p> {version} <p>.mp3}}</p></li> </ul> </li> <li>Database 要存什麼欄位 <ul> <li>至少要定義：</li> <li><tt>guideId</tt></li> <li><tt>spotId</tt></li> <li><tt>language</tt></li> <li><tt>runId</tt></li> <li><tt>storagePath</tt></li> <li><tt>downloadUrl</tt></li> <li><tt>voiceId</tt></li> <li><tt>stylePrompt</tt></li> <li><tt>status</tt></li> <li><tt>createdAt</tt></li> </ul> </li> <li>一次生成是存成「一筆 run + 多個 assets」，還是每個 spot-language 各自一筆 <ul> <li>這會直接影響 history、重生成、active version 切換怎麼做</li> </ul> </li> <li>什麼叫 active-version binding <ul> <li>例如同一個 <tt>spotId + lang</tt> 可能有很多次生成： <ul> <li><tt>run_001</tt></li> <li><tt>run_002</tt></li> <li><tt>run_003</tt></li> </ul> </li> <li>那最後哪一個才是「目前正式採用、要帶去 publish 的版本」？</li> <li>文件有提到 active version 概念，但沒有定義是用哪個欄位存，例如： <ul> <li>在 <tt>spotAudioVersions</tt> 裡某筆 <tt>isActive = true</tt></li> <li>或在 spot document 上存 <tt>activeAudioRunId</tt></li> <li>或在 language-level document 上存 <tt>activeAssetId</tt></li> </ul> </li> </ul> </li> <li>Publish / QA / History 之間怎樣連 <ul> <li>Gate 3 approve 的到底是： <ul> <li>某個 language 的 active version</li> <li>某個 run</li> <li>還是某個 spot-language asset</li> </ul> </li> <li>如果這裡沒定義，後面 <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="LS-94" > <a href="https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-94" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link" title="7.8 Generation History (n8_generation_history)" > <img class="icon" src="https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10315?size=medium" /> LS-94 </a> <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">To Do</span> </span> / <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="LS-95" > <a href="https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-95" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link" title="7.9 Approval Gate 3 UI (Audio Validation)" > <img class="icon" src="https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10315?size=medium" /> LS-95 </a> <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">To Do</span> </span> / <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="LS-96" > <a href="https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-96" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link" title="7.10 Partial Re-Generation Logic" > <img class="icon" src="https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10315?size=medium" /> LS-96 </a> <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">To Do</span> </span> 都會互相打架</li> </ul> </li> </ol> <p><b> <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="LS-92" > <a href="https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-92" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link" title="7.6 Audio Generation (s9_audio_gen)" > <img class="icon" src="https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10315?size=medium" /> LS-92 </a> <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">To Do</span> </span> 目前缺少 generated audio asset 的 canonical schema。請補充 Storage path 規則、DB document 結構、run 與 asset 的關係，以及</b> <tt>spotId + language</tt> <b>的 active version 綁定方式，否則 LS-94/95/96 會無法一致實作。</b></p></comment>
